item.title: Developers
item.description: Easily integrate Storj’s decentralized cloud object storage into your new or existing applications. We recently launched our alpha, enabling developers to run local test networks and begin building applications on top of the Storj platform. Our goal is to decentralize the world’s data and and make cloud storage more affordable. Come and experiment with Storj V3, contribute to its development, and engage with our community. You can also read more in our white paper and public roadmap.
